data.text: Pen ñɨn anɨb ak gapman bɨawl Galili plopens kod mɨdep ak Helod, ne Jisas tɨtay gak takaw ak nɨŋɨd,

bɨ wog gɨñeb ne okok kɨlop agak, Bɨ tap mageptek anɨgup ak, ne bɨ olap ke mel agak. Ne Jon Bɨ Ñɨg Pakñeb anep agak. Nop paklɨnek ak pen, tepayaŋ tɨkjakɨl apɨl mɨdeb tek, nɨŋɨd tap mageptek anɨb okok geb agak.

Pen Jon nop ned nag lɨl, paklɨlak takaw ak, anɨgɨl mɨdeb. Helod ne tɨkjakɨl, nɨmam Pilip bin ne Helodiyas nop ak pɨlɨg dak. Pɨlɨg dek nɨm, Jon agak, Nad bin ak dɨpan, ak teplep ma mɨdeb agak. Anɨb agek, Helod ne agek, bɨne okok kɨli Jon nop dɨl nag tun gɨl, dam nag lɨlak. Helod ne Jon nop pɨsnep paklen kumaŋ agɨl gos nɨgak ak pen, binɨb okok Jon nop bɨ God gos ñek agñeb chɨn agɨlak tek, Helod ne pɨlɨkɨl Jon nop ma paklak.
Pen kɨdek Helod nop nonɨm tɨkak ñɨn ak apek, binɨb ogɨnap apnan gɨl tap ñɨbelak, bin Helodiyas payne ak, apɨl nab anɨb ak kɨgom pagek, Helod nɨgek tep yɨbɨl gak.
Anɨgek, ne pay anɨb anop takaw aglɨl agak, Yad nɨŋɨd agebin, nak tap olap agnɨgenɨgaban, monmon ñɨnɨgayn agak.
Agek, pay anɨb ak, nonɨm agak tek nɨŋɨd anɨb agak, Jon Bɨ Ñɨg Pakñeb kɨmɨg won ak kɨnag adek lɨl, dap ñɨnɨmɨn agak.

Anɨb agek, gapman bɨnonɨm Helod Jon nop nɨgek chɨb gak ak pen, pay anop tap tay yɨp agnɨge ñɨnɨgayn agak tek gos nɨgak. Nɨŋɨd, takaw anɨb ak binɨb okok nɨg yelaknɨŋ agak ak anɨb ak, yɨp nebeŋ ma gɨnɨmuŋ agɨl takaw ne pay nop agak ak kɨdek gak. Bɨ olap agyokek,
14.10 Mat 17.12, Mak 6.27, Luk 9.9 Jon nag lɨ yek ak amɨl, kɨmɨg won nop ak tɨbɨlɨkak.
Tɨbɨlɨkɨl, dɨl kɨnag adek ak lɨl, dapɨl pay anɨb ak nop ñelak, ne pen dad amɨl, nonɨm nop ñak.
Pen Jon nop anɨgɨl kuŋam tɨbɨlɨkelak, bɨne okok apɨl, nop dam kamɨl, am Jisas nop agñɨlak.

Jisas ne Jon nop paklɨlak takaw ak nɨŋɨd, am man wakay olap ke mɨden agɨl bot dɨl, man anɨb ak kelɨgɨl saŋɨdak. Pen binɨb okok, Jisas amnaknɨŋ kɨdek amnun agɨl, taun kɨli okok kelɨgɨlak. Kelɨgɨl, lum adek amɨl, Jisas amnɨg gek okok amnɨlak.
14.14 Mat 9.36, Mak 6.34 Jisas ñɨg gol okok amjakɨl bot ak kelɨgɨl nɨgak, binɨb kuŋay yɨbɨl yelak. Ne kɨlop nɨgek chɨb gak. Pen binɨb kɨli tap gak okok kɨlop gek suŋ lak.

Pen sub saŋɨd amnɨg gaknɨŋ won ak, bɨne okok yek ak apɨl nop agɨlak, Kɨlup apeb, okol man nep nab ak agɨlak. Binɨb kuŋay yɨbɨl okol kɨlop age, man sɨkol okol amɨl, tap mɨdup kɨli ogɨnap tawɨl ñɨŋɨlaŋ agɨlak.
Anɨb agelak kɨlop agak, Taynen amnɨgel agak? Nɨbi ke kɨlop tap mɨdup ñɨnɨmɨb agak.
Agek agɨlak, Chɨn tap mɨdup kuŋay ma mɨdeb, yokɨp bilet anep mamɨd ak, kubsal omɨŋal sek mɨdeb agɨlak.
Agelak Jisas agak, Tap anɨb okok dad owɨm agak.

Anɨb agɨl, binɨb okok kɨlop agek, tap wɨjwɨj adek okok besɨgɨlak. Besɨgel, bilet anep mamɨd ak dɨl, kubsal omɨŋal ak dɨl, kɨlan gɨl nɨŋɨd, God nop tep agɨl, bilet ak tɨpagɨl bɨne okok kɨlop ñaknɨŋ, kɨli dɨlɨg binɨb okok kɨlop bɨlok ñɨlak. Kubsal ak abe gɨlak.
14.20 2 Kin 4.44, Mak 6.42-43, Luk 9.17, Jon 6.11-13 Anɨgɨl bɨlok ñelak, ñɨb gel gel kogmeg gek, dayday kelɨgɨlak okok, bɨne okok wad anep umɨgan ak dɨ yɨgel pɨsnep aplan jakak.
Binɨb anɨb okok mɨdupsek tap ñɨŋɨlak ak pen, bin okok sek, ñapay sɨkol okok sek mel, bɨ okok nep nɨm, 5,000 tek amnak.
Won anɨb ak, Jisas bɨne okok kɨlop ned pɨs adaŋ amnɨlaŋ agɨl, agek bot dɨl saŋɨdɨlak. Saŋɨdɨlaknɨŋ, binɨb okok kɨlop agek nop kelɨgɨl amnɨlak.
14.23 Luk 6.12, 9.28 Amelak, ne ke God nop agɨnɨg, dum alaŋ amnak. Kɨsɨlɨm bad sek owaknɨŋ, ne dum anɨb ak awsek yek.
Pen bɨne okok bot dad ñɨg nab awl sɨŋak amnɨlaknɨŋ, yɨgen apek okdaŋ bot amnak anɨb okok. Yɨgen awl yɨbɨl ak apɨl, ñɨg pag apɨl bot ak tɨg adɨkɨnɨg tek gak.
Pen man tɨkɨnɨg gak won ak, Jisas ñɨg wɨj adek ak tawɨd apɨl, yelak wulep sɨŋak apek nɨgɨlak.
14.26 Luk 24.37 Ñɨg wɨj adek ak tawɨd owak ak nɨŋɨd, ak chɨp kawnan olap apeb agɨl, jel pɨlɨkɨl wal agɨlak.
Won anɨb ak Jisas pen kɨlop agak, Gos sek yenɨmɨb agak. Yad nep apebin, ma pɨlɨkɨnɨmɨb agak.
Agek Pita agak, Bɨawl, nad nep apɨl yɨl, yɨp age, ñɨg wɨj adek ak tawɨd pi ak amnin agak.
14.29 Jon 21.7 Agek Jisas agak, Nad owan agak.
Pen amɨl nɨgak, yɨgen awl yɨbɨl ak apek pɨlɨkek, ñɨg nop dad pi okok amnɨg nep gek agak, Bɨawl, yɨp dan agak.
14.31 Mat 8.26 Anɨb agek, Jisas kasek nop chɨchɨk dɨl agak, Yɨp gos nepan ak pen, taynen gos omɨŋal nepan agak?
Anɨb agɨl, bot mɨgan ak amnɨleknɨŋ, yɨgen awl dek ak kelɨgak.
14.33 Sng 2.7, Mak 4.39, Luk 4.41, Jon 6.69, Apo 8.37, Lom 1.4 Anɨgek nɨŋɨd, bɨne bot mɨgan ayaŋ yelak okok, Jisas yɨb nop dad aplanɨlɨg agɨlak, Nad God Ñɨne yɨbɨl agɨlak.
Pen Jisas ayɨp bɨne ayɨp kɨli ñɨg cheb tɨkɨl man Genesaled pɨs adaŋ amjakɨlak.
Amjakelak, binɨb anɨb okok Jisas nokom owup agɨl, binɨb wulep anɨb okok mɨdupsek suk agel, binɨb tap gak okok dad owlak.

14.36 Mat 9.20-21, Mak 5.27-28, Luk 8.44 Dad apɨl, Jisas nop nebneb gɨlɨg agɨlak, Chɨnop yaw age yɨl, binɨb tap gup okol, chech nep day okok nep dɨnɨgel suŋ laŋ agɨlak. Agelak yaw agek, binɨb nop dɨnɨgɨlak okok kɨlop mɨdupsek suŋ lak.
